        <h3 style="color:var(--text-main); margin-bottom:15px;"><i class="fa-solid fa-bell" style="color:var(--gold);"></i> Your Notifications (Hire Requests)</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--muted); font-size:13px; margin-bottom:20px;">View all pending and received Hire Requests here.</p>
